<!--
  --- Question 68 ---
  This component represents the sixty-eighth question in the quiz.
-->

<div class="question-card" id="card-67" data-qid="67" data-type="single">
  <div class="card-header">
    <span class="q-number">Q 68</span>
    <span class="q-tag single">Single Choice</span>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="question-text">
      Refer to the exhibit. If Host1 were to transfer a file to the server, what layers of the TCP/IP model would be used?
    </p>
    <div class="options" id="opts-67">
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="0">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">A</span>
        <span class="opt-text">only application, Internet, and network access layers</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="1">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">B</span>
        <span class="opt-text">only application, transport, network, data link, and physical layers</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="2">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">C</span>
        <span class="opt-text">application, session, transport, network, data link, and physical layers</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="3">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">D</span>
        <span class="opt-text">only application and Internet layers</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="4">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">E</span>
        <span class="opt-text">application, transport, Internet, and network access layers</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="5">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">F</span>
        <span class="opt-text">only Internet and network access layers</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="submit-wrap" style="display: none;">
      <button class="submit-btn" id="submit-67" disabled>Submit Answer</button>
    </div>

    <div class="explanation" id="exp-67">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-verdict" id="verdict-67"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-body">
        The TCP/IP model contains the application, transport, internet, and network access layers. A file transfer uses the FTP application layer protocol. The data would move from the application layer through all of the layers of the model and across the network to the file server.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pagination-controls">
      <button class="nav-btn" id="prev-67">Previous</button>
      <span class="page-indicator">68 / 70</span>
      <button class="nav-btn" id="next-67">Next</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
